properties.expression: function locatorUpperPath_3b() {        function calcTang(side0, side1, point0, point1, point2, fac, inTan) {            const ang1 = Math.atan2(point2[1] - point1[1], point2[0] - point1[0]);            const ang0 = Math.atan2(point1[1] - point0[1], point1[0] - point0[0]);            const p2relY = point2[1] - point0[1];            const p2relX = point2[0] - point0[0];            const pointDistance = (p2relX * (point1[1] - point0[1]) - p2relY * (point1[0] - point0[0])) / Math.max(Math.sqrt(p2relX * p2relX + p2relY * p2relY), 0.0001);            const perpDist = easeOut(Math.abs(pointDistance), 0, length(point2, point0) / 2, 1, 0);            const centDist = easeIn(Math.abs(side0 - side1), 0, length(point0, point2), 0, 1);            const tangShorten = 1 - perpDist * centDist;            const avang = (ang0 + ang1) / 2;            const leng = inTan === true ? length(point0, point1) * fac * tangShorten : length(point1, point2) * fac * tangShorten;            const pointSide = Number(((point2[0] - point0[0]) * (point1[1] - point0[1]) - (point2[1] - point0[1]) * (point1[0] - point0[0])).toFixed(2));            const flipTang = inTan === true ? (pointSide >= 0 ? 1 : -1) * (Math.sign(Number((ang1 - ang0).toFixed(6))) === 1 ? 1 : -1) : (pointSide <= 0 ? -1 : 1) * (Math.sign(Number((ang0 - ang1).toFixed(6))) === 1 ? 1 : -1);            return [Math.cos(avang) * leng * flipTang, Math.sin(avang) * leng * flipTang];        }        const endctrl = thisComp.layer('{{ end }}');        const curveLinArr = mul(endctrl('ADBE Effect Parade')('Pseudo/skl_3bone_data_01')('curvature').value, 0.01);        if (curveLinArr[1] === 0) {            return createPath([                endctrl('ADBE Effect Parade')('Pseudo/skl_3bone_data_01')('p0').value,                endctrl('ADBE Effect Parade')('Pseudo/skl_3bone_data_01')('p1ikfkfreek').value,            ], [], [], false);        }        else {            const p0 = endctrl('ADBE Effect Parade')('Pseudo/skl_3bone_data_01')('p0').value;            const p1ikfkfreek = endctrl('ADBE Effect Parade')('Pseudo/skl_3bone_data_01')('p1ikfkfreek').value;            const p2ikfkfreek = endctrl('ADBE Effect Parade')('Pseudo/skl_3bone_data_01')('p2ikfkfreek').value;            const ikfkfreeksides = endctrl('ADBE Effect Parade')('Pseudo/skl_3bone_data_01')('ikfkfreeksides').value;            const inTangs = [                [0, 0],                calcTang(ikfkfreeksides[0], ikfkfreeksides[1], p0, p1ikfkfreek, p2ikfkfreek, curveLinArr[1], true),            ];            const outTangs = [                [0, 0],                calcTang(ikfkfreeksides[1], ikfkfreeksides[0], p0, p1ikfkfreek, p2ikfkfreek, curveLinArr[1], false),            ];            return createPath([p0, p1ikfkfreek], inTangs, outTangs, false);        }    }locatorUpperPath_3b();
